caption.center: The People of the State of Illinois, defendant in error, v. Jacob Heitz,

court.center: Appellate Court of Illinois, Second District.

opinion.posture:
Prosecution for violation of liquor law. Defendant convicted.
Error to the County Court of Bureau county; the Hon. James R. Pritchard, Judge, presiding. Heard in this court at the April term, 1925.
opinion.attorneys: Josef T. Skinner and J.L. Spaulding, for plaintiff in error. Carey R. Johnson, for defendant in error.
opinion.opinion_byline: Mr. Presiding Justice Jones delivered the opinion of the court.
